<h4>Ambi Dextrous  (Best Technocrat)</h4>
<p>Dextrous means to be cunning or clever. Because this is what is needed to survive in this age of tough competition, it is the most suitable name. Since this is a new event that we are introducing, no one will be having much knowledge about it. </p>
<p>A technocrat is a person of technical expertise. The competition is similar to the Best Manager competitions conducted during most technical or management based competitions. The various rounds will put the contesetants through tests of varous skills and in the final round the technical knowledge of the contestent is valuated before arriving at a winner. </p>
<p>Preliminaries will be conducted before the contesetants are out to the finals. The total prize money is Rs 5000/- </p>
